<i>môžem dobre žiť.

279
00:26:41,760 --> 00:26:44,110
<i>Mal som vždy to,

280
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:47,710
<i>čo som chcel?

281
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:50,890
<i>V mojom živote som ani raz...

282
00:26:51,740 --> 00:26:55,700
<i>nebol sebecký ani chamtivý.

283
00:26:55,700 --> 00:26:57,890
<i>To, čo chcem,

284
