<i>to, čo chcem robiť,

285
00:27:00,020 --> 00:27:03,750
<i>to, po čom túžim, 

286
00:27:03,750 --> 00:27:06,840
<i>som už niekedy mal,

287
00:27:06,840 --> 00:27:09,570
<i>aspoň raz v celom mojom živote?

288
